Shanty starts up.
It looks to find the root of the project by traversing upwards until it finds a .shanty.yml. If not found, bail.
It creates or updates an index of all the files in the shanty project.

Changed Plugin: For any files that have changed or created, find the owning project and add the changed tag.
SBT Plugin: For any config changes, find the owning project and add the changed tag.

---

Git hooks for updating the Shanty checkpoint.
